    "Subsequently, the defined themes were synthesized in a narrative format to address the specific research questions of this study.",
    "An expert survey was conducted using a combination of singlechoice and open-ended questions to gain insights into expert perspectives on Decentralized Science (DeSci).",
    "This section outlines the methods used for expert recruitment, survey characteristics, data collection, data analysis, and data protection.",
    "The following criteria were used to define experts in the context of the qualitative expert survey:",
